        <p>From a technical point of view, the Matomo Tag Manager makes it easier for us to control, manage and trigger various third-party services. As part of these processes, no personal data is transmitted to or collected by the service provider Motomo.</p>
        <p></p><h3 class="text-xl font-bold leading-5 mt-">Matomo</h3>
